<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About PocketLedger</h1>

  <div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none">
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        PocketLedger is an expense tracking application designed specifically for freelancers, solopreneurs, and individuals who need a simple yet powerful way to manage their expenses.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We believe that expense tracking shouldn't be complicated.
        Our goal is to help you spend less time on bookkeeping and more time on what matters most to you.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why PocketLedger?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        As freelancers ourselves, we understand the challenges of managing business and personal expenses, especially when tax season arrives.
        Traditional accounting software is often overkill for individual needs, while spreadsheets are tedious and error-prone.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        PocketLedger strikes the perfect balance: powerful enough for professional use, simple enough for daily tracking.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Key Features</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">📊 Expense Tracking</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Easily record and categorize your business and personal expenses with a clean, intuitive interface.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">📎 Receipt Management</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Upload and attach receipt/invoice images and PDFs to your expenses for tax compliance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">🔄 Recurring Expenses</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Set up recurring expenses for subscriptions, rent, and regular bills to save time on data entry.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">📈 Analytics & Reports</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Visualize spending patterns and export data in CSV/PDF format for accountants and tax filing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-pink-50 border border-pink-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">🔒 Secure & Private</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Your data is encrypted and stored securely. We never sell or share your information with third parties.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">🌏 Multi-Language</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Available in Japanese, English, and Chinese to serve freelancers worldwide.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Built for Freelancers</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        PocketLedger is particularly popular among Japanese freelancers (個人事業主) who need to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>Track business expenses for tax deductions (経費)</li>
        <li>Store receipts and invoices (領収書) for compliance</li>
        <li>Separate business and personal expenses</li>
        <li>Generate reports for accountants and tax filing (確定申告)</li>
        <li>Manage recurring expenses like office rent and subscriptions</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Whether you're a designer, developer, consultant, writer, or any type of independent professional, PocketLedger adapts to your workflow.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Technology</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        PocketLedger is built with modern, reliable technology:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>Ruby on Rails 8.0 for robust backend infrastructure</li>
        <li>Hotwire (Turbo + Stimulus) for fast, responsive user experience</li>
        <li>Secure file storage with Active Storage</li>
        <li>Industry-standard encryption and security practices</li>
        <li>Mobile-responsive design that works on any device</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Open Source</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        PocketLedger is open-source software released under the AGPL-3.0 license.
        We believe in transparency and community-driven development.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        View our code on GitHub: <%= link_to "github.com/pocketledger/pocketledger", "https://github.com/pocketledger/pocketledger", class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener" %>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Get Started</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Ready to simplify your expense tracking?
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <%= link_to "Sign Up Free", new_user_registration_path, class: "px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition" %>
        <%= link_to "Contact Support", support_path, class: "px-6 py-3 bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-gray-300 transition" %>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 text-center">
    <%= link_to "← Back to Home", root_path, class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" %>
  </div>
</div>
